reviewText: Love love love these movies. Having them all together is amazing. I love this collection!!!
I can't wait to watch my favorite love movies again. I have watched all of the movies, but not as a set. I'm excited!!!
Bought to add to my collection.
great movie, enjoy watching with my family!!

I love "Ever After". And I enjoy watching "Moulin Rouge". So I got this combo pack for those movies. I saw this version Romeo and Juliet a long time ago and can't get myself to watch it again. I will say I am happy for buying the pack still even if I don't watch all of the movies from it.
I loved the movie collection. It was all great romantic movies.  The casing was tattered, but I didn't matter to be. Great movies are great movies.
